Package: spaero
Title: Software for Project AERO
Version: 0.6.0
Authors@R: person("Eamon", "O'Dea", email = "odea35@gmail.com", role =
        c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements methods for anticipating the emergence and
        eradication of infectious diseases from surveillance time
        series. Also provides support for computational experiments
        testing the performance of such methods.
